text: Kampong Panchor Murai (Malay for Panchor Murai Village) is a village in the south-western part of Brunei-Muara District, Brunei, within the mukim (subdistrict) of Pengkalan Batu. The postcode for Kampong Panchor Murai is BH3123. == Geography == As a subdivision, Kampong Panchor Murai borders Kampong Batong to the north, Kampong Parit to the north-east, Kampong Parit to the east, Kampong Pengkalan Batu to the south-east, Kampong Wasan and Kampong Imang to the south, and Kampong Maraburong in Tutong District to the west. == References == Panchor Murai
